{"commentv2": 1, "number": 11, "id": 937200, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "durok", "body": "Highlord Tirion Fordring's Gear:\n\n-He wears the (almost) complete set of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?itemset=681]Lightbringer[/url] - Paladin tier 6, without the helm.\n-Tabard: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=46874]Argent Crusader's Tabard[/url]\n-Cloak: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=41607]Cloak of the Moon[/url] (There are more models like these)\n- Weapon: Ofcourse, [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=13262]the Ashbringer[/url], which is not availible to players ingame.\n\nWhere to get these items:\n-Lightbringer Tier: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?zone=3606#drops:50+1]Hyjal Summit[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?zone=3959]The Black Temple[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?zone=4075]and for the wrist, waist and boots: Sunwell Plateau[/url].\n-Tabard: The tabard has multiple requirements;\n[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?achievement=2817]Exalted Champion of the Alliance[/url] or [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?achievement=2816]Exalted Champion of the Horde[/url], depends on your faction;\n[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?achievement=945]The Argent Champion[/url];\nand 50 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=44990]Champion's Seals[/url]. \n*So this will reward you with Ambassador, of <every capital>, the Argent Champion and Crusader\n-Cloak: This is the most easy part; just create [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=56014]Cloak of the Moon[/url].\n-[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=13262]The Ashbringer[/url]: I'm sorry, one cannot obtain this weapon. You can go for [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22691]Currupted Ashbringer[/url]. Although you'll look like a Death Knight Holy Paladin (WTF?) Corrupted Ashbringer is not availible to players no longer.\nHappy grinding!", "date": "2010-01-04T08:20:38-06:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "you could NEVER get ashbringer, only corrupted version, otherwise 100% correct   and could somebody post screeny with that gear? and if your uber, corrupted ashbringer?", "creationdate": "2010-01-31T21:58:13-06:00", "id": 146328, "rating": 1, "commentid": 937200, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "212003", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "[url=http://coolspot77.com/zarbus/naxxramas%20models/naxx%20CORRUPT%20ASHBRINGER.jpg]Corrupted Ashbringer[/url] The gear: look at this page: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=31044#modelviewer]3d Model Viewer[/url] [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=31044#screenshots:id=99754]Tirion Fordring Screenshot[/url]", "creationdate": "2010-02-14T06:13:34-06:00", "id": 149033, "rating": 1, "commentid": 937200, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "durok", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-04-07T10:22:25-05:00", 2, "durok"]}
