{"commentv2": 1, "number": 15, "id": 1750372, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "ChickNourish", "body": "A more accurate transmog model than durok's, if you want to match the look (please vote this up so people can see):\n\n- Head: None, he is not wearing a helm.\n- Shoulders: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=30998]Lightbringer[/url] (Mother Shahraz - BT)\n- Cloak: As stated, [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=41607]Cloak of the Moon[/url] (a [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=51356#comments]blue PvP cloak[/url] has the same model)\n- Chest: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=30991]Lightbringer[/url] (T6 - Illidan, but it doesn't even show beneath the tabby)\n- Tabard: It's actually the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=43154]Argent Crusade[/url] (standard, faction one, not the argent tournament one)\n- Bracers: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=32279]The Seeker's Wristguards[/url] (Shade of Akama - BT)\n- Gloves: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=30985]Lightbringer[/url] (Azgalor - MH)\n- Belt: The exact match is the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=30897]Girdle of Hope[/url] (Azgalor in MH), although the ones on [url=http://www.wowhead.com/transmog-set=581]this page[/url] are solid standins, but not perfect matches. He's NOT wearing the T6 belt.\n- Legs: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=30995]Lightbringer[/url] (Illidari Council - BT)\n- Boots: One of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=32245]these[/url] [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=32243]two[/url] (Naj'Entus - BT)\n\nNow, for tanks, I recommend [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=19351]Maladath[/url] (BWL - Broodlord) and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=34675]Sunward Crest[/url] (Shattered Sun Offensive exalted). You can grab [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=34609]Kael's sword[/url], it doesn't fit my taste, but the colors do match. And if you're a lucky oldschooler, definitely [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=77561]this[/url].\n\nI'm out of good ideas for Retri, but holy can grab [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=28771]this beauty[/url] and rock it with the shield. If you're a lucky oldschooler, no doubt you will wield [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22691]this[/url] and make me jelly.\n\nP.S. for the T6 pieces it doesn't matter whether you have healer/dps/tank ones, they all look the same.", "date": "2012-10-25T17:01:25-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2012-10-28T11:13:49-05:00", 1, "ChickNourish"]}
