{"commentv2": 1, "number": 24, "id": 1492553, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "ontera", "body": "Upon defeating the first two \"The Damned\" Tirion Fordring says: \"This is our final stand. What happens here will echo through the ages. Regardless of outcome they will know that we fought with honor. We fought for the freedom and safety of our people. Remember heroes; Fear is your greatest enemy in these foul halls. Steel your hearts and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. And fall at the light of righteousness that envelops them. Our march upon Icecrown Citadel begins now!", "date": "2011-08-11T11:49:33-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
