{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 120434, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "64538", "body": "he is a 63 elite,\r\ni met him outside the tower while doing this quest (http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=9443)\r\nhe is fighting a lvl63 elite and 3 or 4 lvl 61 elite scarlet mobs.\r\nand he pwns them all....i saw him still has about 70% health after he killed them all.", "date": "2007-07-14T07:00:58-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 136659, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "46584", "body": "He is normally standing outside his house on the East side of the river between the Eastern and Western Plaguelands. He can sometimes be found just outside Hearthglen if someone is at the end of the very long quest chain he starts, although he has a slightly different name and title.\r\n\r\nHe offers a nice set of three grinding quests at the beginning, which can be pretty handy while you're levelling (Demon Dogs, Carrion Grubbage and Blood Tinged Skies), which lead on to a long and arduous quest chain through various instances and elite zones - during which you find out who he actually is, and why he lives alone in EPL.\r\n\r\n*SPOILER ALERT*\r\n\r\nTirion has been confirmed as the leader of the resurrected Order of the Silver Hand in Northrend, and will be involved in the continuation of the Ashbringer story arc as well as other important events in the expansion.", "date": "2007-08-12T19:04:54-05:00", "rating": 46, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
