{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 453692, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Soulskulptor", "body": "He is Tirion Fordring, Former lord of the town of Hearthglen. He was a proud paladin of the Silver Hand, until he came across an orc (name will withheld to avoid spoilers of the story) and engaged it in battle. However, a noble act of the orc caused Tirion to question what was common thinking about what the orcs were, which led to his exilement.\r\n\r\nmore details can be found in the story, \"Of Blood and Honor.\"", "date": "2008-11-18T15:04:31-06:00", "rating": 15, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Just out of curiosity, why did you withhold the orc's name for spoiler reasons if you were going to give away the entire plot of the book and subsequent quest lines?", "creationdate": "2009-01-24T21:35:50-06:00", "id": 75235, "rating": 22, "commentid": 453692, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Windriver", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The orc's name is Eitrigg, you can find him in Grommash Hold in Org.", "creationdate": "2009-01-28T22:43:13-06:00", "id": 76305, "rating": 11, "commentid": 453692, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Meatwad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "[b]dont ruin it![/b]", "creationdate": "2009-01-31T23:15:30-06:00", "id": 385116, "rating": 0, "commentid": 453692, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "250546", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "And actually you can find him not just in Org, but in [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=28244]Zul'Drak[/url] as of WotLK. :)  Fordring asks Thrall specifically if he can come to Northrend in his [url=http:/