{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 141344, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "mattous", "body": "[quote]During a panel at BlizzCon 2007, Chris Metzen and Alex Afrasiabi talked about a questline in Northrend focusing on Tirion Fordring. They mentioned plans to include the Ashbringer in the questline, though at such an early stage of production the Ashbringer's inclusion may not be final.\n\nDuring the hands-on demo of Wrath of the Lich King at BlizzCon, doing a small quest chain about a sacred artifact leads you to a \"Cleric of the Silver Hand\". The cleric reveals himself to be Tirion, now known as Highlord Tirion Fordring of the Order of the Silver Hand - attired in Lightbringer Armor, and holding the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=13262]Ashbringer[/url]. He shouts a challenge to Arthas, saying that the Silver Hand was coming for him and that his kingdom would crumble beneath the weight of justice.[/quote]\n\nThe above quote was taken from the [url=http://www.wowwiki.com]wowwiki[/url] page on Tirion Fordring any of the information here may or may not end up in the expansion but it seems logical that with Arthas being the main focus in the next expansion that the Ashbringer will also play a big part.\n\nFor more information on Tirion Fordring then see [url=http://www.wowwiki.com/Tirion_Fordring]this page[/url] on wowwiki.\n\n[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=20349]Tirion Fordring[/url] can also be found in [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?zone=2367]Old Hillsbrad Foothills[/url] in the Caverns of Time he can be seen disscussing the Ashbringer with fellow members of the Silver Hand.", "date": "2007-08-20T18:54:58-05:00", "rating": 20, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "from that same article, it says he will be placed at \"the port of Valgarde in Northrend's Howling Fjord\". according to blizzard, thats the only alliance base in Northrend. so how is the horde gonna complete the chain if they gotta 'raid' an alliance town to talk to him?", "creationdate": "2007-10-06T19:24:34-05:00", "id": 313043, "rating": 0, "commentid": 141344, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Spectrezh", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2007-08-20T19:06:07-05:00", 2, "mattous"]}
