{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 477253, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Archivist", "body": "This particular instance of Highlord Tirion Fordring is for the quest [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=13403]Tirion's Gambit[/url]. After obtaining [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=44784]Cultist Acolyte's Hood[/url] from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=32507]Cultist Acolytes[/url] in the area (and thusly using it) you speak to him to begin a rather lore pivotal event.", "date": "2008-11-29T03:25:14-06:00", "rating": 13, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
